{"tid":1894542,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"英國獨立黨黨魁Nigel Farage：英國脫歐唔係爲咗向北京叩頭，保守黨必須對華爲一事反抗","createTime":"2020-02-24T04:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T11:41:28.000Z","uid":131691,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9bc2c8a362a60cdabeb6bfe69c3b02818bcf3032","tid":1894542,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:00:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newsweek.com/huawei-boris-johnson-conservative-rebellion-churchill-farage-1488582\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Fhuawei-boris-johnson-conservative-rebellion-churchill-farage-1488582&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=ed998a40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newsweek.com/huawei-boris-johnson-conservative-rebellion-churchill-farage-1488582</a><br />\n<br />\n==背景==<br />\nNigel Farage可以話係英國近年政治史上最風雲嘅一個人物，佢雖然冇做過英國國會議員（淨係做歐盟議會議員），但係環繞住佢嘅政治魅力同民意影響，將「脫歐」變成「對現有腐敗政治系統嚟個大清洗」嘅代名詞，促成咗英國成功脫歐。<br />\n<br />\nNigel Farage係玩煽情路線嘅本土+民粹派，對歐盟嘅指控有平民在意嘅民生（e.g. 移民對醫療及綜援等等社會資源嘅搶奪），有中產在意嘅文化（e.g. 移民溝淡英國本土文化，甚至移民唔識講英文），有學者在意嘅主權（e.g. 歐盟議會及法庭並非英國公民選出，但係主權凌駕於英國議會及法庭）。雖然佢嘅煽情民粹路線令到唔少人覺得佢低俗搞破壞，但係政治學上嚟講，Nigel Farage其實係現代政治上少有真係貫徹始終有理念嘅政客（現代大部分政客都係搭順風車嘅騎牆中間派centrists）。<br />\n<br />\n對華爲事件，Nigel Farage嘅取態貫徹佢一向嘅作風：任何動搖英國主權嘅嘢，都要破壞，包括其實係中國政府延伸嘅華爲。<br />\n<br />\n2020年1月尾，Nigel Farage上過電台講香港政府隱瞞疫情。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ggu0UwdSdD0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGgu0UwdSdD0&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=85b34622\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ggu0UwdSdD0</a>"},{"pid":"b4eae5cb89429bfb760e76aa23d50d9da646489d","tid":1894542,"uid":91432,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"能反共的就是盟友<br />\n除了白癡左膠"},{"pid":"8cbc75c5000b151d357a673e02b8b4116d4b0ef9","tid":1894542,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e20991b5654ba55cf1735bfca7238f231b54f5","tid":1894542,"uid":248290,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:06:03.000Z","msg":"日落 奶得咁開心 <br />\n邊敢反<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbaecdc2d29aa1a457910b8706e61b48b2423c6","tid":1894542,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4985af42ea455de88a3854a1bf07072122c8cec","tid":1894542,"uid":3513,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:08:51.000Z","msg":"Sunset <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413ce3230c0c9aaf6b129514695be499a128013b","tid":1894542,"uid":60451,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"冇啦<br />\n冇得救啦"},{"pid":"201b1be629010a6b28746364802c5bca8b65331f","tid":1894542,"uid":131691,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f9e20991b5654ba55cf1735bfca7238f231b54f5","tid":1894542,"uid":248290,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:06:03.000Z","msg":"日落 奶得咁開心 <br />\n邊敢反<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:10:40.000Z","msg":"睇Farage唔係睇現有英國政權「夠唔夠膽」，<br />\n係睇Farage今次能夠掀起幾多英國人因爲華爲一事對現有英國政權作出足夠嘅政治威脅。"},{"pid":"9ad7ed2d15ce80f27535f151ce129e773c5d0e45","tid":1894542,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0155b58551e93d4dc48cf5e28d46af0fe990102","tid":1894542,"uid":202577,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4ea